H0.text: In which British city is the Jewry Wall Museum. Leicester

H1.text: In which British city is the Jewry Wall Museum. York

H2.text: In which British city is the Jewry Wall Museum. Lincoln

H3.text: In which British city is the Jewry Wall Museum. Caerlyr

A4.text: The remains of the baths of Roman Leicester can be seen at the Jewry Wall; recovered artifacts are displayed at the adjacent museum.

A5.text: Some sites, such as Leicester Castle and the Jewry Wall, are both scheduled monuments and listed buildings.
